Reasoning: 
- cs.RO (Robotics) is the most likely category as the paper focuses on robot learning for deformable object manipulation. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper uses deep reinforcement learning algorithms. 
- cs.CV (Computer Vision) is relevant as the agents need to perceive the state of the cloth in order to manipulate it. 
- cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is relevant as the paper explores the use of end-to-end learning for deformable object manipulation. 
- cs.SY (Systems and Control) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with control of a robotic system.
